use GeoModelInterfaces GeoModelInterfaces-* DetectorDescription/GeoModel
use LArG4RunControl    LArG4RunControl-*    LArCalorimeter/LArG4
use LArHV              LArHV-*              LArCalorimeter/LArGeoModel
